Title: Unplanned unexplored..just keep exploring
DateModified: '2018-02-21'
DatePublished: '2018-04-20'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2018/applications/unplanned-unexplored-just-keep-exploring
SetInCountry: Malaysia
Category: The last thing I expected
AuthorName: Vinay Mishra
AuthorCountry: India
Text: "We 2 families just wanted to go any place out of india, 4 adults n 3 kids..so\
  \ air ticket to malaysia were in budget though just one month before we booked..we\
  \ booked for 1st day at KL n after that we wanted to explore whatever it feels ..so\
  \ one more day at KL n then we moved to langkawi.road..ferry..hired vehicle ...amazing\
  \ place n amazing beauty..island hoping ..beaches ..pure joy..then moved for cameron\
  \ highlands..on way stay at one hotel ..where we could see local bride n saw one\
  \ marriage..cameron highland was real adventure..online booked hotel was difficult\
  \ to find..it was a apartment ..at mid 12 night no food..luckily one grocery store\
  \ open..so maggi..bread n milk was the dinner..apartment was of a chinese..arranged\
  \ by a nepali hotel staff...food from malaysia n we indians staying there\u263A\
  .....then moved to KL..danced on a sqaure in kl on an indian song..sung by a bangladeshi\
  \ n music by a malasian...overall return safely\U0001F60A"
